(6,	1,	'2025-02-28 18:51:38',	'2025-02-28 18:51:38',	'<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>WordPress is a powerful and widely used content management system (CMS) that allows users to create and manage websites with ease. WordPress is highly customizable, offering thousands of themes for design and plugins to extend functionality, making it suitable for blogs, business websites, e-commerce stores, portfolios, and more. It is also SEO-friendly, scalable, and secure, with regular updates to enhance performance and safety.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Whether you are a beginner or an advanced developer, WordPress provides a flexible and user-friendly solution for building websites without needing to code from scratch.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Getting Started with LocalWP</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:group {\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\",\"flexWrap\":\"nowrap\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:group {\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\",\"flexWrap\":\"nowrap\",\"orientation\":\"horizontal\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":75,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://homepage-assignment-1.local/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/pexels-markus-winkler-1430818-12220444-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-75\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>To streamline my learning process, I used <strong>LocalWP</strong>, a powerful local development environment for WordPress. LocalWP makes it easy to set up a WordPress site on my computer without needing an online server. It offers features like <strong>one-click installations, database management, and SSL support</strong>, making development faster and more efficient.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Understanding WordPress Editors</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\",\"flexWrap\":\"nowrap\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":72,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://homepage-assignment-1.local/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/pexels-caio-56759-1024x681.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-72\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\",\"orientation\":\"vertical\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:group {\"className\":\"wp-block-col\",\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group wp-block-col\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>WordPress offers different ways to create and manage content:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Block Editor (Gutenberg)</strong> – The default editor that provides a drag-and-drop experience with content blocks. It allows for visually structured content creation.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Classic Editor</strong> – A simple, traditional text-based editor resembling a Word-like interface, perfect for those who prefer a minimal editing experience.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Advanced Custom Fields (ACF)</strong> – A powerful plugin that lets developers create custom fields for posts, pages, and custom post types. This is particularly useful for dynamic and structured content that requires more flexibility than the default editor provides.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Understanding Posts and Menus</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\",\"flexWrap\":\"nowrap\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":73,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://homepage-assignment-1.local/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/pexels-kevin-ku-92347-577585-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-73\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I learned how to create and organize <strong>posts</strong> using categories and tags, helping in better content organization. I also explored <strong>WordPress Menus</strong>, which allow for easy navigation customization, enabling users to structure their websites efficiently.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->',	'Wordpress',	'',	'publish',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'homepage',	'',	'',	'2025-02-28 22:37:30',	'2025-02-28 22:37:30',	'',	0,	'http://homepage-assignment-1.local/?page_id=6',	0,	'page',	'',	0),
(7,	1,	'2025-02-28 18:51:38',	'2025-02-28 18:51:38',	'<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hi, I\'m Arshnoor Singh! I\'m currently learning WordPress and exploring web development. Passionate about building dynamic and user-friendly websites, I\'m on a journey to enhance my skills and create meaningful digital experiences. Stay tuned as I share my progress and projects!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->',	'Homepage',	'',	'inherit',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'6-revision-v1',	'',	'',	'2025-02-28 18:51:38',	'2025-02-28 18:51:38',	'',	6,	'http://homepage-assignment-1.local/?p=7',	0,	'revision',	'',	0),
